|  OVERVIEW  Arcadia, informally referred to by outsiders as the *Dome*, is a sprawling megalopolis located on the Atlantic coast of North America. It is the largest urban civilization in the country, as well as the most populous, harboring over 150 million residents across 105,000 sq mi (as of 2150). It is one of 15 Earth conurbations which have resulted from the amalgamation of Anomalous and Corporeal populations and one of 165 total conurbations (including the Earth-Mars interplanetary region and the spacelands surrounding both). The megalopolis is divided into six large metropolitan areas called “boroughs”, each deeply embedded with its own CULTURE and GRAVITAS. This guide will detail all six boroughs, so you, our newest resident, can decide which of them and their districts fits your flair\!
